    <item>
      <title>纽约慈善机构利用私人信贷作为新财富来源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/private-credit-tapped-by-nyc-charity-as-new-source-of-wealth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约的慈善机构一直在寻找下一代华尔街领袖来支持他们。对于在布朗克斯和东哈莱姆经营特许学校的 Dream 来说，寻找的地方很明显：快速发展的私人信贷领域，该领域正在为其后起之秀创造数十亿美元的新财富。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/private-credit-tapped-by-nyc-charity-as-new-source-of-wealth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 16:57:09 GMT</pubDate>
